  "system": {
    "description": "<p>The eldest child and the one most likely to do something his mother hasn't planned for. Caden's suit — AEGIS-03 — is optimised for velocity above all else. He hits fast, repositions faster, and is genuinely difficult to pin down. He and his father are competitive in the way that only similar people can be, and he chafes under Nadia's command structure even as he respects it. The most publicly visible Forgeborn member.</p>",
